precis:
Amendment to the UNITED STATES TARIFF RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS which
amends section XVI of the Schedule so as to provide the same FTA tariff
treatment to diesel engines as to reciprocating piston engines thus
eliminating an anomaly in the current rules of origin.
